, demanded that women should be able to study art at the Royal\nSwedish Academy of Arts on the same terms as men. This demand was met in 1864.\n","linknr":126,"url":"Sofia_Adlersparre","recorded":1375086949,"links":["/w/index.php?title=Sofia_Adlersparre&action=edit","/w/index.php?title=Sofia_Adlersparre&action=edit","//bits.wikimedia.org/favicon/wikipedia.ico","/w/opensearch_desc.php","//en.wikipedia.org/w/api.php?action=rsd","//creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/","/w/index.php?title=Special:RecentChanges&feed=atom","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=ext.gadget.DRN-wizard%2CReferenceTooltips%2Ccharinsert%2Cteahouse%7Cext.rtlcite%2Cwikihiero%7Cext.uls.nojs%7Cmediawiki.legacy.commonPrint%2Cshared%7Cmw.PopUpMediaTransform%7Cskins.vector&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=site&only=styles&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/en.wikipedia.org/load.php?debug=false&lang=en&modules=startup&only=scripts&skin=vector&*","//bits.wikimedia.org/geoiplookup","//meta.wikimedia.org","#mw-navigation","#p-search","/wiki/Sophie_Adlersparre","/wiki/File:Sofia_Adlersparre_self_portrait.jpg","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/Sofia_Adlersparre_self_portrait.jpg/220px-Sofia_Adlersparre_self_portrait.jpg","/wiki/File:Sofia_Adlersparre_self_portrait.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.22wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","/wiki/File:Josephine_of_Leuchtenberg_by_Adlersparre.jpg","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/da/Josephine_of_Leuchtenberg_by_Adlersparre.jpg/220px-Josephine_of_Leuchtenberg_by_Adlersparre.jpg","/wiki/File:Josephine_of_Leuchtenberg_by_Adlersparre.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.22wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","/wiki/Josephine_of_Leuchtenberg","/w/index.php?title=Axel_Adlersparre&action=edit&redlink=1","/wiki/%C3%96land","//sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carl_Gustaf_Qvarnstr%C3%B6m","/wiki/Johan_Gustaf_Sandberg","/